reviewText: Fun work out! I take my video with me when on vacation!

I thought I'd like to try some dance moves as a workout for a change of pace.  I've tried the dance dvd a few times, but find myself going back to the Leslie Sansone videos.  The second dvd is good and a bit of a challenge.  The problem is that it goes very quickly from standing, to weights, and to floor exercises very quickly.  A person has to be quite nimble in order to be ready for each quick change.
